nodes.text: A video store was, presumably, a business that rented holodramas. They were common on the planet Coruscant, where billboards and signs were put up in order to advertise them, and attract potential customers. One such advertisement was written in Aurebesh, and read "VIDEO STORE" - "KL FKJ GD" - "FAD FA FED". While defending Duchess Satine Kryze from an assassination attempt, Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi threw the Death Watch assassin into the advertisement, prompting the assassin to activate his jetpack and retreat.
One video store was known as Pawp.
